Standards-Version: 3.6.1.1

Package: libgchemutils0
Architecture: any
Section: libs
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}
Description: GNOME chemistry utils (library)
 The GNOME Chemistry Utils provide C++ classes and Gtk+-2 widgets
 related to chemistry. They will be used in future versions of both
 gcrystal and gchempaint.
 .
 See http://www.nongnu.org/gchemutils/.
 .
 This package contains the shared library.

Package: libgchemutils-dev
Architecture: any
Section: libdevel
Depends: libgchemutils0 (>= ${Source-Version})
Suggests: libgchemutils-doc
Description: GNOME chemistry utils (development version)
 The GNOME Chemistry Utils provide C++ classes and Gtk+-2 widgets
 related to chemistry. They will be used in future versions of both
 gcrystal and gchempaint.
 .
 See http://www.nongnu.org/gchemutils/.
 .
 This package contains the static library and the header files.

Package: libgchemutils-doc
Architecture: any
