Package: gchemutils
Architecture: any
Section: misc
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}
Conflicts: libgchemutils-data
Replaces: libgchemutils-data
Suggests: chemicalmime
Description: GNOME chemistry utils (common test files and binaries)
 The GNOME Chemistry Utils provide C++ classes and Gtk+-2 widgets
 related to chemistry. They will be used in future versions of both
 gcrystal and gchempaint.
 .
 See http://www.nongnu.org/gchemutils/.
 .
 This package contains some common files for testing the runtime libraries.
